<bibRefCitation author="Bogutskaya" pageId="2" pageNumber="67" refString="Bogutskaya, N. G. &amp; Naseka, A. M. (2004) Catalogue of agnathans and fishes of fresh and brackish waters of Russia with comments on nomenclature and taxonomy. KMK Scientific Press, Moscow, 389 pp. [in Russian with English summary]" type="book" year="2004">Bogutskaya &amp; Naseka 2004</bibRefCitation>
